Our Privacy Policy explains
What information we collect and why we collect it.
How we use that information.
Information we collect
We collect information to provide better services to all of our users â€“ from figuring out basic stuff like where is your current township, to more complex things like which send you the notification that you reserved. We collect information in the following ways:
Location information:
When you use our services, we may collect and process information about your actual location. We use Google technologies to determine your location.
Unique application numbers:
Certain services include a unique application number. This number and information about your installation (for example, the operating system type and application version number) may be sent to servers when you install or uninstall that service or when that service periodically contacts our servers, such as for notifications.
How we use information we collect
We use information collected to improve your user experience and the overall quality of our services such as more relevant notification service. We will not use your information for any commercial purpose.
Quick Login with your Apple (iOS), Google, facebook Account
After you login with your account then you can do "Weather Checkin-In", we only use your "email" to identify you, do not request for other information or priviliage from your account.
Delete already-logined Apple (iOS), Google, facebook Account and data
If you want to delete your logined account and data, please refer to the following screenshots below, in our App click the "Logout" button from our "Login Service" page, then we will delete your account and data from our App immediately. But we will keep some history record for auditing usage only.
